---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Contact Baijiu365';
const description = 'Contact Baijiu365 about corrections, baijiu questions, editorial suggestions, and future partnerships.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <header class="article-header"><div class="narrow"><p class="eyebrow">Contact</p><h1>Contact</h1><p class="lede">Send corrections, topic suggestions, and practical baijiu questions.</p></div></header>
  <section class="content"><article>
    <p>For now, use the public project contact route through ChinaTripBox or future Baijiu365 contact channels. Please include the page URL, what you believe should change, and any source or first-hand context that helps verify the issue.</p>
    <h2>Good Reasons To Get In Touch</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>A correction to a factual, brand, label, or buying-risk detail.</li>
      <li>A beginner question that would make a useful guide.</li>
      <li>A source suggestion for overseas retail, label reading, or food pairing context.</li>
      <li>A disclosure question before any commercial relationship is introduced.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="callout"><strong>Note:</strong> Baijiu365 does not currently sell baijiu, appraise bottles, or authenticate individual purchases.</div>
  </article></section>
</BaseLayout>
